  "body": "Created a values.yaml file with the following:\r\n```\r\nlabels:\r\n  tier: frontend\r\n  foo: bar\r\n  foo3: bar3\r\n```\r\n\r\nand a template with the following:\r\n```\r\napiVersion: v1\r\nkind: ConfigMap\r\nmetadata:\r\n  name: \"bug bug\"\r\ndata:\r\n{{- if .Values.labels }}\r\n{{ toYaml .Values.labels | indent 2 }}{{- end }}\r\n  bug: yes\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhen I run a dry run it returns:\r\n```\r\n[debug] Created tunnel using local port: '41519'\r\n\r\n[debug] SERVER: \"127.0.0.1:41519\"\r\n\r\n[debug] Original chart version: \"\"\r\n[debug] CHART PATH: /home/me/bug\r\n\r\nNAME:   eponymous-whale\r\nREVISION: 1\r\nRELEASED: Wed Feb  7 13:35:39 2018\r\nCHART: bug-0.1.0\r\nUSER-SUPPLIED VALUES:\r\n{}\r\n\r\nCOMPUTED VALUES:\r\nlabels:\r\n  foo: bar\r\n  foo3: bar3\r\n  tier: frontend\r\n\r\nHOOKS:\r\nMANIFEST:\r\n\r\n---\r\n# Source: bug/templates/bug-configmap.yaml\r\napiVersion: v1\r\nkind: ConfigMap\r\nmetadata:\r\n  name: \"bug bug\"\r\ndata:\r\n  foo: bar\r\n  foo3: bar3\r\n  tier: frontend\r\n\r\n  bug: yes\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe empty line above `bug: yes` has the 2 spaces from the indent but the `{{- end }}` should have removed them (or better yet not passed back the extra line from the toyaml function\r\n```\r\nhelm version\r\nClient: &version.Version{SemVer:\"v2.8.0\", GitCommit:\"14af25f1de6832228539259b821949d20069a222\", GitTreeState:\"clean\"}\r\nServer: &version.Version{SemVer:\"v2.8.0\", GitCommit:\"14af25f1de6832228539259b821949d20069a222\", GitTreeState:\"clean\"}\r\n```",
